Kanayamahiko-no-Kami is enshrined in shrines across Japan, including {{ill|Nangū Taisha|ja|南宮大社|12=draft}} (dedicated solely to Kanayamahiko-no-Kami) in {{ill|Tarui, Gifu|ja|垂井町|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nangu Otabi Shrine|ja|南宮御旅神社|12=draft}} (dedicated solely to Kanayamahime-no-Kami), {{ill|Kanayago Shrine|ja|金屋子神社|12=draft}} in {{ill|Yasugi, Shimane|ja|安来市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Koganeyama Shrine (Ishinomaki)|ja|黄金山神社 (石巻市)|12=draft}} on {{ill|Kinkasan|ja|金華山 (宮城県)|12=draft}} in {{ill|Ishinomaki, Miyagi|ja|石巻市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Mikane Shrine|ja|御金神社|12=draft}} in {{ill|Kyoto|ja|京都市|12=draft}}, and {{ill|Hari Shrine|ja|針神社|12=draft}}, a subsidiary shrine of {{ill|Hataeda Hachiman Shrine|ja|幡枝八幡宮|12=draft}}.

